Section 11-103.6 of Title 70 of the Oklahoma Statutes and has the
1
2
appropriate level of rigor.
2
3
2. By January 31, 2027, the Department shall publish on its
3
4
website the first-grade mathematics curriculum approved pursuant to
4
5
paragraph 1 of this subsection.
5
6
F. The consortium shall review curriculum for additional grade-
6
7
level subject areas in accordance with a schedule adopted by the
7
8
consortium, in collaboration with the Department.
8
